00:13:08,042 --> 00:13:10,645
in order to focus consistently on the Pokemon.

290
00:13:11,593 --> 00:13:15,434
And then you have things like our games like Nintendo's Zelda Breath of the Wild

291
00:13:16,054 --> 00:13:19,315
where the minimal flat design allows the player to focus on Link,

292
00:13:19,475 --> 00:13:23,716
to focus on his inventory, which plays a huge part of the adventurous world within the game.

