00:15:33,416 --> 00:15:35,659
but simultaneously promote the game spirit

335
00:15:35,699 --> 00:15:37,201
of being a fast-paced action game.

336
00:15:39,597 --> 00:15:43,822
So, in short, there is so much you can explore in these phases

