00:16:52,012 --> 00:16:54,994
Perhaps due to color or more visual iteration

360
00:16:55,114 --> 00:16:56,415
in a decoration.

361
00:16:57,036 --> 00:16:58,297
You could be distracting the player

362
00:16:58,337 --> 00:16:59,878
from the content you're presenting to them.

363
00:17:01,299 --> 00:17:01,900
Personality.

