00:17:02,494 --> 00:17:06,076
Can I see my world's keywords when I look at the UI,

365
00:17:06,777 --> 00:17:09,298
even without the visual support of characters and environments?

366
00:17:10,239 --> 00:17:12,720
What's important to see is in those games,

367
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:15,762
brands or keywords are visually implied in the design.

368
00:17:15,882 --> 00:17:17,903
So visuals have the ability to stand on their own,

369
00:17:18,103 --> 00:17:19,864
but still reflect the game's brand.

370
00:17:21,625 --> 00:17:22,245
Implication.

371
00:17:22,265 --> 00:17:24,807
Are interactive elements distinct

