00:17:34,974 --> 00:17:37,597
Perhaps color palettes and light iconography

376
00:17:37,797 --> 00:17:39,599
is enough to communicate a brand in a world.

377
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:43,062
Also, I need to make sure that the player can tell

378
00:17:43,102 --> 00:17:45,104
the difference between interactive objects

379
00:17:45,264 --> 00:17:47,066
and non-interactive objects.

380
00:17:48,728 --> 00:17:49,368
And finally, scale.

