00:18:09,913 --> 00:18:14,014
memory load or can't even scale, let's say, from a nine-slicing perspective.

386
00:18:15,698 --> 00:18:18,439
So when you look and start to iterate your designs,

387
00:18:18,679 --> 00:18:21,380
you just need to be judicious about these four categories.

388
00:18:21,961 --> 00:18:23,821
You need a balance between narrative impact

389
00:18:24,021 --> 00:18:24,982
and player usability.

