00:18:26,262 --> 00:18:27,923
Remember, during our process,

391
00:18:28,003 --> 00:18:30,324
how good UI should enhance and promote

392
00:18:30,364 --> 00:18:32,505
a frictionless experience for a player

393
00:18:32,605 --> 00:18:34,126
and the world they are interacting with.

394
00:18:35,542 --> 00:18:38,246
UI is just one of the many visual elements

395
00:18:38,407 --> 00:18:40,089
that can be included in your game.

